    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>CSS transform / transition</h1>\n<p><span style=\"color: skyblue; font-weight: bold\">transform</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>rotate 회전<br>\n각도의 범위는 0~360도. 마이너스 각도는 시계 반대 방향으로 회전</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>scale 확대/축소<br>\n이미지(개체)의 크기를 조절할 수 있으며, 비율을 지정하여 크기를 조절하고 n배로 확대 수치 지정/ 소수점도 가능</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>1.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">scaleX</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> //가로의 3배 확대 / Y로 쓰면 세로의 3배 확대</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>skew 기울임<br>\n주어진 각도로 기울일 수 있으며, X축은 좌/우로 Y축은 상/로 기울이는 효과를 줌</p>\n<ul>\n<li>X축 : + 각도는 우측 / - 각도는 좌측</li>\n<li>Y축 : + 각도는 아래쪽으로 / - 각조는 윗쪽</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">skewX</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>+-10deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>translate 위치이동<br>\n위치를 이동시킬 수 있으며, 좌/우/상/하로 위치 조정<br>\nscale과 마찬가지로 X축, Y축으로 지정 가능</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translateX</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: skyblue; font-weight: bold\">transition</span><br>\n마우스를 클릭하거나 hover 상태에 변화를 줌</p>\n<ul>\n<li>transition-property: 색상이나 위치 등 변화의 대상이 되는 css 속성 지정</li>\n<li>transition-duration: 변화할 때 걸리는 시간을 초단위로 지정</li>\n<li>transition-delay: 변화되기 전 시간을 초단위로 지정</li>\n<li>transition-timing-function: 진행시간 (속성값은 animation 속도형태 속성과 동일)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>한 줄 정의 예시</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> opacity 2s 1s ease<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* transition-property : opaticy */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* transition-duration : 2s */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* transition-delay : 1s */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* transition-timing-function : ease */</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3><strong>참고 링크</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bbol-world.tistory.com/65\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">css3 animation / tranform / transition</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CSS] transform / transition","summary":null,"date":"2021.02.25.","categories":["CSS"],"options":null,"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/7d2ea/background_css.png","srcSet":"/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/7754d/background_css.png 78w,\n/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/56c9a/background_css.png 155w,\n/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/7d2ea/background_css.png 310w","sizes":"(min-width: 310px) 310px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/431a4/background_css.webp 78w,\n/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/0c936/background_css.webp 155w,\n/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/9ee98/background_css.webp 310w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 310px) 310px, 100vw"}]},"width":310,"height":310}},"publicURL":"/static/16d1125cf5156bb060ab5a66c92c70e3/background_css.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2021/2021-02-25-CSS_transform_transition/"}},
